ABSTRACT
A system for secure storage of data includes a key database
and a processor. The processor is configured receive a
request associated with securely storing data and encrypt the
tenant service key using a tenant master key. The data is
encrypted using the tenant service key. The processor is
further configured to encrypt the tenant master key using a
customer key and store encrypted tenant service key and
encrypted tenant master key in the key database.
